{"tid":938262,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"讀書係咪真係咁重要？","createTime":"2018-12-12T07:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T04:38:38.000Z","uid":195223,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"14a3b8dddb154384903fe6f158e3d36ce05fc803","tid":938262,"uid":195223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8568752be87392213bb630e0359cb0041b40e96d","tid":938262,"uid":172507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:22:20.000Z","msg":"都要睇你想做咩"},{"pid":"bcf4b55455d1c0407f5742e726a46f5ae3994e03","tid":938262,"uid":222166,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"呢個時代仲有咩學一門手藝？科技咁撚勁，乜都Ai遲下，班搬運佬起場佬全部收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔讀書食撚得屎"},{"pid":"9fb2cebfa0570867db4ba09883447a278b6575d9","tid":938262,"uid":129506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"唔係,但唔讀書你係咪有另一門手藝先?<br />\n你有其他野叻既咪發展其他野<br />\n冇既就死返去讀書,唔讀書又冇野叻只係代表你懶先唔撚讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a9774dba79671faeb0d2389c43eaad756a5844","tid":938262,"uid":201197,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"你認為乜嘢叫讀書先？<br />\n我只能夠答你，學習係重要囉<br />\n<br />\n我幾十歲人先自學返中學初級物理，藝術，數學，哲學，宗教，歷史，不知幾過癮。學知識係好開心。<br />\n不過我都明白細路仔唔明白學習為何物，而被困在學校做功課考試嗰種無奈。"},{"pid":"487bbf50443d591afa099499a202ee6dd8cb321a","tid":938262,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75a1d544707c13752355cdc5966f447d5f7a1b88","tid":938262,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:39:48.000Z","msg":"細細個唔想讀書岀左黎學師點知做咁多年野就讀足咁多年pt 返學仲辛苦"},{"pid":"003faef7c854b7862e5de83a4875bd51fff4e620","tid":938262,"uid":172385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75a1d544707c13752355cdc5966f447d5f7a1b88","tid":938262,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:39:48.000Z","msg":"細細個唔想讀書岀左黎學師點知做咁多年野就讀足咁多年pt 返學仲辛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:45:25.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59824a5830fb12483d15ded2bf1107d8795f95d1","tid":938262,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T09:19:19.000Z","msg":"睇你讀咩書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人認為讀書 &ne; 報讀正規課程"},{"pid":"3808db02b34e04a89ce8792b6469a7cffe1a131d","tid":938262,"uid":69679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T13:12:32.000Z","msg":"你問吓烏大龜，佢實答你唔L係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa5b484a2a9813e2228c4b59e07b2a0d93d447d","tid":938262,"uid":195223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8568752be87392213bb630e0359cb0041b40e96d","tid":938262,"uid":172507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:22:20.000Z","msg":"都要睇你想做咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"仲未諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知自己想點"},{"pid":"77b4751ffb701281a2e7761a34c2f1fc1d55d93b","tid":938262,"uid":37822,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:28:31.000Z","msg":"識人重要過讀書"},{"pid":"e664cbb9579c28cbb011021518fdba03276331a3","tid":938262,"uid":21699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"487bbf50443d591afa099499a202ee6dd8cb321a","tid":938262,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"bcf4b55455d1c0407f5742e726a46f5ae3994e03","tid":938262,"uid":222166,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"呢個時代仲有咩學一門手藝？科技咁撚勁，乜都Ai遲下，班搬運佬起場佬全部收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔讀書食撚得屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66f1965ee699e8ee682e6cf83f79ba1a8c0a390","tid":938262,"uid":164751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"最起碼要透過學習去明白事理<br />\n繼而係不同領域揾自己興趣，如果有目標又繼續鑽研，你嘅成果亦可能留倒畀之後更多嘅學生同其他人<br />\n唔讀書唔係唔得<br />\n但明顯少咗一截，有好多人基本野係學校無學好，出咗尼做野好耐都未catch up返<br />\n<br />\n有機會同時間就要好好學習<br />\n相信好多過25歲嘅人會明白，思考同學習速度真係愈大愈慢"},{"pid":"dc539e9bc65b71eb54f117be006ee735c32202de","tid":938262,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:40:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8708ff3440a07c4bf8cbe7dd39ae738098c3c819","tid":938262,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:44:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d318967e7dd5a8a6a9a6e54dd7a608c74c461f0f","tid":938262,"uid":139027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52a9774dba79671faeb0d2389c43eaad756a5844","tid":938262,"uid":201197,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"你認為乜嘢叫讀書先？<br />\n我只能夠答你，學習係重要囉<br />\n<br />\n我幾十歲人先自學返中學初級物理，藝術，數學，哲學，宗教，歷史，不知幾過癮。學知識係好開心。<br />\n不過我都明白細路仔唔明白學習為何物，而被困在學校做功課考試嗰種無奈。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:44:56.000Z","msg":"讀書梗係好啦，人有求知慾，當獲得一啲知識嘅時候會開心同埋想繼續學落去。但係問題係有大量嘅功課同測驗考試，我認為呢點先係學生唔願學嘢嘅重點"},{"pid":"dd8deb9aa3780650e5b8c610cb5817b43d327cd6","tid":938262,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c66f1965ee699e8ee682e6cf83f79ba1a8c0a390","tid":938262,"uid":164751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"最起碼要透過學習去明白事理<br />\n繼而係不同領域揾自己興趣，如果有目標又繼續鑽研，你嘅成果亦可能留倒畀之後更多嘅學生同其他人<br />\n唔讀書唔係唔得<br />\n但明顯少咗一截，有好多人基本野係學校無學好，出咗尼做野好耐都未catch up返<br />\n<br />\n有機會同時間就